name: Monkey playing Pong
description: Monkey playing Pong is an animation inspired by Pager the monkey, the new advance in the Neuralink company and its high channel count brain-machine interface fully implanted in Pager's brain to coordinate his neural activity and anticipate movements with his brain signals. and being able to play the classic Atari Pong game with your mind.  Brilliant or terrifying, depending on your point of view.   1920x1080 pixels, 0: 00: 16: 20, 404 frames, 24 fps, 2021. GIF version available.
